Wrapping: bind/collect

Wrapper Classes: these classes are wrapping/collecting/binding a primitive value into 
===============  wrapper class objects.

byte     -    Byte
short    -    Short
int      -    Integer
long     - 	  Long

float    -    Float
double   -    Double

char     -    Character

boolean  -    Boolean

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. we can able get size of the data type(in bytes/bits), max and min values

2. we can do conversions to other types(primitives/object types)
				- AutoBoxing: primitive to object
				- unBoxing: object type to primitive
3. To implement Generics in Java Collections.

